title: 104. Winning Is More Fun Than Fun Is Fun Ft. Ed Mylett
itunes:title: 104. Winning Is More Fun Than Fun Is Fun Ft. Ed Mylett
description:
Winning is more fun than fun is fun. On today's episode, Andy and the crew are joined by Arete Syndicate co-founder and entrepreneur Ed Mylett as they discuss how to create separation from your competition, how to adapt to the forks in the road and what it takes to level up in business and life.
